	<div class="flex container extra-vertical">
		<div class="col-6 right-6">
			<div class="padded">
				<p class="summary">We created a design that puts users' content first.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="left-2 col-10">
			<div class="padded">
				<p>As a newcomer to the market, Roader needed a recognizable visual identity. We explored various visual directions in type, form, and color, to establish a digital design language that made a statement while highlighting unique aspects of the product.</p>
